  /// Identity-footer suffix: 'ep' abbreviates 'endpoint' (a networking id), followed by the shortened endpoint id. Joined to the identity id with a ' · ' separator at the call site — a list of technical facts, not a sentence. Keep it short and lowercase; 'ep' may stay untranslated as a technical abbreviation.
